---

<DocLayout title="Colors">
	<p>Our color system is built on a foundation of primitives that are then mapped to specific semantic tokens for Brand and UI usage.</p>

	<section>
		<h2>Brand Colors</h2>
		<p>Semantic colors used to represent our brand identity and product categories.</p>
		
		<h3>Primary</h3>
		<div class="color-grid">
			{brand.primary.map(c => <ColorSwatch name={c.name} hex={c.hex} token={c.token} />)}
		</div>

		<h3>Category</h3>
		<div class="color-grid">
			{brand.category.map(c => <ColorSwatch name={c.name} hex={c.hex} token={c.token} />)}
		</div>

		<h3>Seasonal</h3>
		<div class="color-grid">
			{brand.seasonal.map(c => <ColorSwatch name={c.name} hex={c.hex} token={c.token} />)}
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>UI Colors</h2>
		<p>Functional colors used for backgrounds, containers, and borders throughout the interface.</p>
		
		<h3>Background</h3>
		<div class="color-grid">
			{ui.background.map(c => <ColorSwatch name={c.name} hex={c.hex} token={c.token} />)}
		</div>

		<h3>Container</h3>
		<div class="color-grid">
			{ui.container.map(c => <ColorSwatch name={c.name} hex={c.hex} token={c.token} />)}
		</div>

		<h3>Stroke</h3>
		<div class="color-grid">
			{ui.stroke.map(c => <ColorSwatch name={c.name} hex={c.hex} token={c.token} />)}
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Primitives</h2>
		<p>The core palette of colors available in our design system.</p>
		
		{Object.entries(primitives).map(([group, colors]) => (
			<div class="primitive-group">
				<h3 class="capitalize">{group}</h3>
				<div class="color-grid">
					{colors.map(c => <ColorSwatch name={c.name} hex={c.hex} />)}
				</div>
			</div>
		))}
	</section>

	<style>
		section {
			margin-top: 60px;
		}
		h2 {
			margin-bottom: 20px;
			border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
			padding-bottom: 10px;
			font-size: 2rem;
			color: #111;
		}
		h3 {
			margin: 40px 0 20px;
			font-size: 1.4rem;
			color: #444;
		}
		.capitalize {
			text-transform: capitalize;
		}
		.color-grid {
			display: flex;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			gap: 30px;
			margin-bottom: 40px;
		}
		.primitive-group {
			margin-bottom: 60px;
		}
	</style>
</DocLayout>
